TEST SIGNED HTTP HEADERS
  ${result} =  Scan Message With Rspamc  ${MESSAGE}  -u  bob@cacophony.za.org  --header=PerformArcSign:yes  --header=DkimDomain:cacophony.za.org  --header=DkimSelector:dkim  --header=DkimPrivateKey:
